574
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:46,680
If he came to join us now

575
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:48,640
and sell the boots together with us,

576
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:51,000
then he'd take our profit.

577
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,280
Of course Qi Tian

578
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,840
won't profit himself

579
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,840
at the expense of his friends.

580
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:01,440
Well,

581
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:03,320
that makes sense too.

582
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:06,160
Tian isn't that kind of person indeed.

583
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:08,560
Heizi, so you mean

584
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,120
he won't join us?

585
00:21:10,120 --> 00:21:12,360
No, he will join us.

586
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:13,560
But not now.

587
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,600
If one day

588
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:17,280
Tian finds a new way

589
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:18,840
to make money,

590
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,560
then he will ask us

591
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,080
to follow him.

592
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:23,320
This is Qi Tian,

593
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,400
our big brother.

594
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,080
True.

595
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,800
Tian knows a lot of people

596
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:30,760
and he's smart too.

597
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,840
Maybe he can really
find ways to make money

598
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,800
that are beyond our imagination.

599
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,200
Folks,

600
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,960
hang in there.

601
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,280
Just wait.

602
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,960
When Tian

603
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:43,960
gets the knack

604
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:46,520
of doing business,

605
00:21:46,520 --> 00:21:49,280
we're not far away from getting rich.

606
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,400
Military boots!

607
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,920
You scared me.

608
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:57,960
- What's wrong with you?
- Military boots!

609
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,960
- Military boots!
- Military boots!

610
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,080
Madam, have a look at our military boots!

611
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,440
- Come and have a look!
- Military boots!

612
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:06,000
Lower your head
or you may hit it on the branches.

613
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,120
Okay.

614
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,200
We've looked around for a day

615
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,880
and I don't see any ways to make money.

616
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:16,680
That's enough.

617
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:21,080
I mean, it has only been one day.

618
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:22,440
If the ways to make money

619
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:24,440
could be learned in one day,

620
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:25,800
then everyone would be rich.

621
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,240
Then what?

622
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:29,160
Should I ask for another leave tomorrow

623
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,640
to accompany you again?

624
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:32,280
The ancients said,

625
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:36,200
victory is ensured when you
know both yourself and the enemy.

626
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:38,560
Our ancestors couldn't lie to us.

627
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:40,800
This is also the rule of business.

628
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:42,680
You have to understand the market,

629
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,400
know what is easy to buy and easy to sell,

630
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:45,360
and what is lucrative

631
00:22:45,560 --> 00:22:47,280
before taking actions.

632
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,760
It's so complicated.
I can't understand it anyway.

633
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:53,320
Then I'll just listen to you.

634
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:56,560
Actually,

635
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,800
I'm not that sure

636
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:00,800
either.

637
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:02,560
Well,

638
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:04,400
let me think about it further

639
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:06,160
then we can discuss it.

640
00:23:07,760 --> 00:23:08,800
Let's discuss it tomorrow.

641
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:09,880
Time for you to go home now.

642
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,800
I'll also go to bed.

643
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:13,800
Take care on your way back.

644
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,840
He Hongling! There's a call for you!

645
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:38,720
Hongling, a call for you.

646
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:39,880
A call for me?

647
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,680
You're the only one
who has numerous calls.

648
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:43,320
Is this the platoon leader

649
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,240
or that childhood friend?

650
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,640
Okay, stop it.

651
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,080
Go, Hongling.

652
00:23:54,480 --> 00:23:55,160
Hello,

653
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:56,000
this is He Hongling.

654
00:23:56,280 --> 00:23:58,480
Hongling, this is Uncle Dong.

655
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,040
Your mother had another heart attack,

656
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,840
and she's in 301 Hospital.

657
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:27,600
Guohua, my mom had another heart attack.

658
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:29,360
The doctor said
she had to have surgery right now.

659
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,480
Can you please contact

660
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:32,800
that Professor Su
you mentioned last time for me?

661
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:33,800
I'll make a call now!

662
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,000
Okay, thank you.

663
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:35,980
(Work Notes)

664
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:42,320
Guohua, last time we were in the queue

665
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:44,040
for about two weeks
before seeing Professor Su.

666
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,480
However, this time my mom is
in urgent need for treatment,

667
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:47,280
we can't wait this long.
What should we do?

668
00:24:48,120 --> 00:24:50,040
Don't worry.
Even if Professor Su is unavailable,

669
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:51,480
there will be other doctors for sure.

670
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,080
Now we're in a much better place,

671
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,680
there will be better doctors
to treat your mom for sure.

672
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:55,360
Don't worry.

673
00:25:14,040 --> 00:25:15,000
I regret it so much.

674
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,200
I shouldn't have refused your help then.

675
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,160
When you're in Beijing,

676
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,440
contact me anytime if you need help.

677
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,440
I'm always here.

678
00:25:49,580 --> 00:25:51,900
(In use Silent Operating Room)

679
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,640
Uncle Dong!

680
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:57,200
You're back.

681
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:58,280
How's my mom?

682
00:25:59,760 --> 00:26:01,120
She's inside.

683
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:03,280
How long will it take?

684
00:26:05,040 --> 00:26:05,720
It should be fast.

685
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:08,560
Don't worry, she will be okay.

686
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:09,800
Thank you, Uncle.

687
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:29,640
Isn't this Comrade Xiao?

688
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:30,840
Are you here to see Hongling?

689
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:32,800
Right. Today we have a day off,

690
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:33,880
so I asked Hongling

691
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,520
to go to the bookstore
in the city together.

692
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,440
Go to the bookstore?

693
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:37,800
Today?

694
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:39,080
You don't know it yet?

695
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:40,480
What happened?

696
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,320
Hongling left for home yesterday,

697
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,720
she's not here now.

698
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,320
What do you mean?

699
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:46,920
So you really don't know it?

700
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:49,080
I heard that her mom suddenly fell ill

701
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:50,520
and had to have surgery immediately.

702
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,400
So she went back to Beijing in a hurry.

703
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,640
Wait!

704
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,400
Report!

705
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:10,840
Come in!

706
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:15,360
Guohua, I heard
Hongling returned to Beijing yesterday.

707
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:17,160
Her mom was hospitalized
and had to have surgery.

708
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,280
Do you know that?

709
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,920
Chunsheng, sit down.

710
00:27:22,080 --> 00:27:23,880
After contacting the doctor for her,

711
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:25,480
I took Hongling directly to the airport.

712
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,080
I was in such a hurry

713
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:27,040
that I forgot to tell you.

714
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,240
Don't worry,

715
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:30,120
her mom's surgery was a success.

716
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:30,960
No worries.

717
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,840
The surgery was a success?

718
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,920
You arranged this?

719
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,160
Last time her mom was ill,

720
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,600
I contacted Professor Su for Hongling.

721
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:44,760
So this time, she came straight to me,

722
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,720
asking me if I could call Professor Su.

723
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,160
Professor Su happened to be attending
a meeting in Guangzhou,

724
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,880
so I found

725
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:51,840
another good doctor for her.

726
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:56,400
Chunsheng,

727
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:58,720
are you angry with me?

728
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,400
How can I be angry with you?

729
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:04,280
If not for you,

730
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:06,360
Hongling's mom couldn't have
got the surgery this quickly.

731
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:08,680
This is cardiac surgery

732
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:10,320
and is highly difficult.

733
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:11,600
I understand.

734
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:18,160
Guess you've stayed up all night too.

735
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,760
Have a rest.

736
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,840
I'll leave now.

737
00:28:22,120 --> 00:28:22,720
Okay.

738
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,320
Guohua,

739
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:30,800
can you tell me
the phone number of the hospital?

740
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,160
I'll write it down for you.

741
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:46,360
Okay. Have a good rest.

742
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:47,640
Goodbye.

743
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:05,460
(Nurse Station)

744
00:29:07,440 --> 00:29:08,040
Hello?

745
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,440
Hello, is this Hongling?

746
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,000
This is Chunsheng speaking.

747
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:13,160
Chunsheng, how did you know this number?

748
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,560
I just went to your dormitory to see you,

749
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:17,520
and your comrade-in-arms told me
that you returned to Beijing yesterday.

750
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,320
So I went to see Guohua in a hurry.

751
00:29:20,080 --> 00:29:20,760
I'm sorry.

752
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,480
I was too anxious yesterday

753
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,400
and forgot to tell you this.

754
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:24,920
It's okay.

755
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:25,720
Oh,

756
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:26,840
how's your mom?

757
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,040
She's doing well.

758
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:30,200
The doctor Guohua found is excellent.

759
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:32,040
The nurses here told me

760
00:29:32,040 --> 00:29:33,440
that in Beijing, he and
Professor Su are the only ones

761
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:36,000
who can perform
valve replacement surgery.

762
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:38,680
At first, my mom's surgery could
only be scheduled for next month,

763
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,120
however, another patient

764
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:41,600
failed the preoperative
evaluation yesterday

765
00:29:41,600 --> 00:29:42,360
and had to wait further,

766
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:43,800
so my mom got the place instead.

767
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:46,920
We really have to thank Guohua for this.

768
00:29:48,480 --> 00:29:49,360
Oh, and Uncle Dong too.

769
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,760
My mom hasn't been
feeling well these days

770
00:29:51,800 --> 00:29:53,240
and she complained to Uncle Dong.

771
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:55,040
Fortunately, he remembered it.

772
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:58,480
He went to my home to check on her,

773
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,800
and after knocking for a while,
nobody answered.

774
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:03,280
He was afraid that something
might go wrong, so he forced his way in

775
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:05,040
and found that my mom
had fainted on the ground.

776
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:06,960
He took her to the hospital immediately.

777
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:09,280
Fortunately, your mom is doing well now.

778
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:10,280
Well,

779
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,400
I'll thank Uncle Dong later.

780
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,520
Hongling,

781
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,040
how much

782
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:21,560
did the surgery cost?

783
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:24,440
1,500 yuan.

784
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,280
The follow-up treatment in hospital

785
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,760
will cost about
one or two thousand at least.

786
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:32,280
Guohua said he'd pay it for me,
but I declined.

787
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:34,960
It's okay, Hongling.

788
00:30:35,280 --> 00:30:36,040
Take it easy.

789
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:37,960
Take good care of your mom

790
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:40,720
and I'll take care of the rest.

791
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:43,800
In a word,

792
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,200
trust me.

793
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:47,440
We can overcome any problems.

794
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:50,560
Okay. I'll wait for your call.

795
00:30:52,520 --> 00:30:53,320
By the way, Hongling,

796
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:54,720
you...

797
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:56,560
Look after yourself.

798
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:58,760
Don't get exhausted.

799
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:17,900
(Reception Office)

800
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:24,720
Hello, Yanqiu.

801
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,280
It's me, Chunsheng.

802
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:27,520
Yanqiu, I wonder

803
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:31,160
how much money we have now.

804
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:32,560
What happened?

805
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:34,520
Um...

806
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,040
It's...

807
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:37,200
It's Hongling.

808
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:39,320
Her mom is hospitalized

809
00:31:39,320 --> 00:31:40,200
and had surgery.

810
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,240
I'm afraid it will cost

811
00:31:42,560 --> 00:31:44,960
nearly 4,000 yuan in total.

812
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,520
That's too much.

813
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:49,160
How can we afford it?

814
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,400
Yanqiu, calm down, please.

815
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:52,640
Just tell me
how much money we have now.

816
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,320
I'll find a way to get the rest.

817
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,200
The rest of your salary

818
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:59,240
plus the money
you sent home from the army

819
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,040
are about 400 yuan.

820
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:03,040
A while ago, Dad received
800 yuan in back pay.

821
00:32:03,560 --> 00:32:05,880
We don't have much money other than that.

822
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,720
My factory is not doing well now

823
00:32:09,040 --> 00:32:10,800
and I gave the money
I received in back pay a while ago

824
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:13,560
to Qi Tian for his business.

825
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:15,960
I see.

826
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:17,040
Yanqiu,

827
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:19,040
can you lump the money

828
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:20,560
you have now together?

829
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:21,760
I'll find a way

830
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:24,000
to get the rest,

831
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,080
okay?

832
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:25,840
Oh, by the way,

833
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:28,800
her mom is in 301 Hospital.

834
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,520
Bed No. 34.

835
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:30,960
Yes, I see.

836
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:37,340
(Be vigilant to defend our country)

837
00:32:48,520 --> 00:32:49,560
Nice skills.

838
00:33:14,120 --> 00:33:14,880
No need

839
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:16,280
to pretend.

840
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:17,640
We know you need money.

841
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:18,040
Exactly.

842
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,600
No need to be this upset.

843
00:33:24,360 --> 00:33:26,240
No, I can't accept this.

844
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,240
Amao has a whole family

845
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:29,120
to support.

846
00:33:29,760 --> 00:33:31,600
And Lei's elderly mother lives alone.

847
00:33:31,600 --> 00:33:32,640
I know it well.

848
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,280
As for Jinzhu...

849
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:35,280
Enough.

850
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:37,200
You weren't this sentimental before.

851
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:39,080
We send money home regularly,

852
00:33:39,320 --> 00:33:40,800
it won't hurt much.

853
00:33:41,080 --> 00:33:42,120
Focus on your own business.

854
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,240
Count it.

